is also played. After the standard} a5 ({Alekhine's} 9... c5 {is also good:}
10. bxc5 bxc5 11. Rb1 Qc8 12. Qb3 Ba6 13. Bb2 Nbd7 14. Rfc1 Rb8 15. Qa2 dxc4
16. Nxc4 Bb7 $132 {Laketic - Lanzani, Milan 2000}) 10. b5 c6 ({Black is also
