Rb1 (12. cxd5 exd5 $11) 12... a4 $5 (12... Ba6 $5 {Kelires - Gevorgyan,
Paleochora 2017}) 13. cxd5 exd5 14. Qc2 Re8 {the position is roughly balanced.
