Qb2 Ba6 16. Ne5 (16. Re1 Bd6 $11) 16... Qc8 17. Ndf3 Ne4 18. Nxc6 Qxc6 19. Ne5
Qe6 $11) 9... exd5 10. b4 {The most usual continuation, trying to gain space
on the queenside. Alternatives are:} ({a)} 10. Ne5 c5 11. b3 (11. dxc5 bxc5 $13
