{[#] TEST 24 - What's Black's best move in his fight for equality?} 8... Be7 $1
({Instead,} 8... Nbd7 {is the most common move in practice, but after} 9. Re1 {
I think that White has an unpleasant initiative in lines like} dxc4 10. Nxc4
Bd5 11. Nfe5 Bxg2 12. Kxg2 Rc8 13. Bg5 Be7 14. e4 $1) 9. Re1 {(For other moves
see chapter 12) isn't dangerous here, because after} dxc4 10. Nxc4 Bd5 11. Nfe5
(11. Nce5 O-O 12. dxc5 Bxc5 13. Nd3 Be7 $11) 11... Bxg2 12. Kxg2 Qd5+ {(Black
lacks this resource in the line 8...Nbd7) Black even has some initiative.} *

